# Backlog tasks

Use [backlogs/_task.template.md](../../backlogs/_task.template.md) and [INVEST](../../.notebook/00_references/invest.md).

## Task types

`feature` | `bugfix` | `refactor` | `deploy`

## Status gates

- `draft` — after `analyze-intake-to-task`
- `ready` — INVEST complete, AC + estimation + test plan, human approved
- `in-progress` — after design links (M+) or human waiver for XS/S
- `done` — verification evidence + delivery report when handover required

## Skills

- New draft from intake: `analyze-intake-to-task`
- Harden / split: `planning-and-task-breakdown`
- Catalog alignment: `spec-driven-development`
- Design: `basic-design`, `detail-design`

See [backlogs/README.md](../../backlogs/README.md).
